videos.description: Tom Brady receives a loud ovation when he's introduced to the crowd at Michigan.

videos.headline: Fumble return TD gives Colorado double-digit lead
videos.description: Chidobe Awuzie forces a fumble and Derek McCartney recovers to give Colorado a 14-point lead over Michigan.

videos.headline: Wolverines get back in it thanks to blocked punt
videos.description: Michigan blocks a Colorado punt and Grant Perry returns it for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Colorado QB Liufau throws 70-yard TD on injured leg
videos.description: Colorado QB Sefo Liufau finds Shay Fields for a 70-yard touchdown while hurt and after taking a big hit on the play to give the Buffaloes a 28-24 lead.

videos.headline: Michigan takes lead on 42-yard TD run
